Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我昨天买的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:24.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是运动系社团经常拿来练习握力的帅气道具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喔  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,体积那么小  无论在哪都能练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要练握力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:39.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你又没有参加社团  练了有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  只是觉得它帅气就买了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不不  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,握力增强以后能做很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:52.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喔？ 比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能拔出瓶塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:57.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用开瓶器不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:00.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能吊挂很久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吊在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能捏碎苹果…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:04.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么要捏碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  就是能做很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:14.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说  你停下来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:26.02,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}目が合うずっと前から まっすぐ見ていたのよ
