Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:03:02.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一二…一二…一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:03.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是在数拍子而已  我自己打着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是  是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:17.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一二…一二…一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:21.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我懂了高木同学  这是挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:25.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果跟不上高木同学数拍子的节奏  就是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是这么回事儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明我要消耗力气  高木同学却只要动动嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不管怎么看  对我都是压倒性不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:58.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一二…一二…一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她的节奏变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  这么快的节奏下高木同学也撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明是自己发起的挑战  你反而要输了啊  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一定要坚持住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:07.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一二…一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:11.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:16.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我终于赢了高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你刚刚好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我真的赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:28.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  刚刚根本就不是在比拼输赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:29.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  这才是她的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,让我精疲力尽之后再和我比握力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你太天真了高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算已经累得不行了  但我怎么可能输给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想借一下你的握力器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还以为你要和我比握力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:07.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的手  还没牵够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在这里  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你找的高木同学  是这位高木同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是这位高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:17.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么是这位高木同学吗  还是这位高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,心动子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给大家介绍一下转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家好  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,心动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到我身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的手是这只哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哞  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:11.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  居然这样捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  咩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说啊  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:24.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,攻击对手的弱点可不是卑鄙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,连丹迪都出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是战略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,砰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:42.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,现在还是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来我一边做作业一边练握力  然后睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨天的夏日祭也是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我连做梦都被高木同学捉弄了
