Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是我们夏日祭以后第一次见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我之前在梦里也见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完了  说了不该说的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真荣幸啊  是什么样的梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不记得了  我一醒就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是色色的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  你不是说忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你找我有什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明天不都开学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很急的事儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在这之前  你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么  那陪我走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:59.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  要是能更长一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,暑假很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我昨天游了个痛快  被晒成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我前几天也去海边了  只晒成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,糟糕  提到晒伤的话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果高木同学知道我的后背被晒得火辣辣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,晒伤果然很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一下子就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  我决不能在这时露怯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一点都不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我再拍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我骗你的啦  疼死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办  太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话还会被她拍  你是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你来猜猜看我今天为什么来找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你猜对的话  我就不碰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:21.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算我说不碰你  你也不会放心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那当作比赛的话你就能接受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,, 好  我参加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:41.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  是为了还我借给你的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:45.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为你猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有这种规则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  请说下一个答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:01.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,仔细想想  高木同学不是两手空空的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  看她一脸高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都不知道别人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  你叫我出来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是想要捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜…猜错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一半猜对一半猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一半？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要用一半的力气拍你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了算了  还是别了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟我也猜对一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  不会拍你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说了我不会对西片撒谎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那刚才的比赛都没意义了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:16.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后呢  猜错的一半是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比你刚刚的回答来得更简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,更简单？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:32.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且  我的事从刚才就已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是想见我而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,知道答案了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有  完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这怎么说得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真…真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有什么一闪而过的答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片会不会也出现在我的梦里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那样的话  即使在梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也能捉弄西片了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨天被老妈叫去除草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就晒成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是逊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我用了这个皮肤用胶带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,即使在炎热的日子里也是个绅士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们好空虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,晒黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,晒黑而已  你也太大惊小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,紫外线是皮肤的大敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,晒黑后放着不管不护理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,听说皮肤很快就会变得皱皱巴巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吓死个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:09.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我暑假每天都在外面遛狗或者去帮忙干农活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我每天也在参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家会一起变成老奶奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:24.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好  用对皮肤有好处的东西自制面膜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,先从酸奶开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有效果了  有效果了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你们俩也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  那不是给独角仙吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像这样将黄瓜切成薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:42.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再贴在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的会有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,黄瓜加点蜂蜜好像会变成蜜瓜的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,张嘴  友加里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哈？ 要我尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么味道  什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像蜜瓜的味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,黄瓜加了蜂蜜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然酸奶还得加蜂蜜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的面膜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早啊  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天开始就是第二学期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了对了  我有东西要给高木同学看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:49.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,接招吧  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛  又是惊吓盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道你把做作业的时间都拿去做这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来我猜中了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:11.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你也就现在能笑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要问为什么  这个「惊吓盒·改  dinosaur」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟至今为止的玩意儿不是一个等级的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会有什么出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这里头可不只有纸和棉花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有恐龙在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为西片你刚才自己说出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「惊吓盒·改  dinosaur」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,dinosaur是恐龙的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:45.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来西片你不知道 dinosaur 的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:51.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还觉得是个有恐龙的感觉  念起来很帅的词…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真有西片的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:57.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算知道里面是恐龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这次的也很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是来真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那如果我打开这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样叫出声的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是西片赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有像这样被吓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算我赢行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的  这场比赛我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我赢了就请我喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:30.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还没打开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们一起看了烟花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:07.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么时候他才会对我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早啊  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:11.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天开始就是第二学期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实为了庆祝新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我给高木同学准备了个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,惊吓盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这可是我拿做作业的时间做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:44.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为猜中了是惊吓盒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又没有要跟你比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这就算扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:56.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,梦里输掉的事就当没发生咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:18.67,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夢でもし逢えたら　素敵なことね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:27.61,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あなたに逢えるまで　眠り続けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:36.36,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あなたは私から　遠く離れているけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:42.88,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}逢いたくなったら　瞼を閉じるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:51.42,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夢でもし逢えたら　素敵なことね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:23:00.82,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あなたに逢えるまで　眠り続けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:06.04,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今も私　枕抱えて眠っているの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.88,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしも　もしも逢えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:14.33,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}その時は　力いっぱい私を抱きしめてね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:16.37,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:25.90,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夢でもし逢えたら　素敵なことね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:33.86,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あなたに逢えるまで　眠り続けたい
