Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:36.36,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}虽然你我相隔甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:42.88,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想要见你的时候  就会闭上双眼
